# ğŸ§  FeelIt - Opinion Analysis on Reddit

**FeelIt** is a web application developed as a Final Degree Project to analyze opinions on any topic collected from Reddit, presenting a summarized and clear view through sentiment analysis and highlighted comments.

---

## ğŸ” Features

- âœ… Search for desired topics
- âœ… Extraction and visualization of relevant comments
- âœ… Sentiment classification (positiu, negatiu, neutre)
- âœ… Loading bar with animation and icons
- âœ… Informative pages (`About`, `Contact`, `NotFound`)
- âœ… Responsive StickyNavbar navigation
- âœ… Scroll locked only on the home page

